FOR A LONG TIME.

08:14.994 --> 08:17.371
OKEY-DOKEY?

08:17.455 --> 08:21.250
SO, THEN, SHE WALKS
OVER TO THE COUNTER AND...

08:21.334 --> 08:23.461
{\an1}Heffer:
HOLD IT!

08:23.544 --> 08:24.670
WHAT?!

08:24.754 --> 08:26.214
HMM...

08:26.297 --> 08:29.634
YOU KNOW, I WAS THINKING...

08:29.717 --> 08:32.135
YES?

08:34.304 --> 08:35.847
DO WE REALLY NEED
THE CHEESE AT ALL?

08:35.932 --> 08:38.433
WHAT?

08:38.517 --> 08:40.269
{\an1}WHY, YOU
BIG STUPID COW.

08:40.352 --> 08:41.604
WHAT DID I SAY?

08:41.687 --> 08:43.688
{\an1}WHY DO YOU
TORMENT ME LIKE THIS?

08:43.773 --> 08:45.107
I'M NOT ATTACKING YOU

08:45.191 --> 08:47.443
I'M ATTACKING YOUR
STUPID OLD IDEAS.

08:47.526 --> 08:52.114
"STEP 47 TO STEP 7,212.

08:52.198 --> 08:55.117
DRAW LOTS AND LOTS
OF LITTLE PICTURES."

09:14.512 --> 09:16.347
(<i> groaning</i> )

09:16.430 --> 09:17.807
WHAT?

09:17.890 --> 09:18.140
(<i> clicking and whirring</i> )

09:18.224 --> 09:20.643
NEXT ONE.

09:21.602 --> 09:24.105
(<i> clicking and whirring</i> )

09:24.188 --> 09:25.856
NEXT ONE.

09:26.565 --> 09:29.360
(<i> clicking and whirring</i> )

09:29.735 --> 09:32.697
ALL WE HAVE TO DO IS
EDIT THE FILM AND WE'RE DONE.

09:33.823 --> 09:38.160
{\an5}Filburt:
STUPID? STUPID?
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK?

09:38.244 --> 09:41.664
THE CHEESE MONOLOGUE
IS STUPID, FILBURT!

09:41.747 --> 09:44.083
LONG AND STUPID.

09:44.166 --> 09:44.959
OH, YEAH?

09:45.042 --> 09:47.503
{\an1}YOU KNOW
THE SALAMI CHASE SEQUENCE?

09:47.586 --> 09:49.672
YOU KNOW WHAT
I THINK OF THAT?

09:49.755 --> 09:51.716
{\an3}THERE...

09:51.799 --> 09:53.009
{\an3}YEAH...

09:53.092 --> 09:55.386
{\an1}OH, YEAH?

09:55.469 --> 09:57.680
{\an1}WELL, YOU KNOW THE
BIG CHEESE CLIMAX ENDING?

10:00.099 --> 10:01.267
(<i> clanging</i> )

10:01.350 --> 10:04.854
(<i> breathing heavily</i> )

10:04.937 --> 10:05.479
(<i> crashing</i> )

10:05.563 --> 10:07.523
Heffer:
YOU STUPID LIAR!

10:07.606 --> 10:08.691
YOU CALL YOURSELF
AN ANIMATOR?

10:08.774 --> 10:11.986
{\an4}Filburt:
KEEP YOUR STINKING PAWS
OFF MY CELLULOID.

10:12.069 --> 10:15.990
{\an4}Heffer:
YOUR CARTOON'S NOT FUNNY ENOUGH
TO BE ON THE FAMILY CHANNEL!

10:16.073 --> 10:20.494
(<i> screaming</i> )

10:20.578 --> 10:23.998
(<i> Ralph clears his throat</i> )

10:24.081 --> 10:24.915
HEY, GUYS.

10:24.999 --> 10:27.877
JUST CAME BY
TO PICK UP THE FINISHED FILM.

10:27.960 --> 10:31.339
I'LL GIVE YOU A COUPLE OF
MINUTES TO WRAP THINGS UP.

10:32.465 --> 10:36.719
(<i> crashing and banging</i> )

10:36.802 --> 10:40.097
(<i> yelling and mumbling</i> )

10:40.181 --> 10:41.724
(<i> drilling</i> )

10:41.807 --> 10:42.183
HERE IT IS.

10:42.266 --> 10:44.226
GREAT, GREAT.

10:44.310 --> 10:47.063
I'LL ZIP THIS
ON OVER TO THE EXECUTIVES.

10:47.146 --> 10:48.189
THANKS A BUNCH.

10:48.272 --> 10:49.398
LET ME SAY BEFORE WE START

10:49.482 --> 10:51.067
THAT I'M VERY HAPPY WITH THIS.

10:51.150 --> 10:52.068
IT'S ABOUT...

10:52.151 --> 10:53.277
DELI MEATS.

10:53.361 --> 10:55.112
Both:
DELI MEATS?

10:55.196 --> 10:56.906
{\an1}AND IF YOU
PICK THIS UP

10:56.989 --> 11:01.077
FOR 893 EPISODES,
YOU'LL GET MORE OF THE SAME.

11:01.160 --> 11:03.704
OKAY, HIT THE LIGHTS.

11:03.788 --> 11:05.498
(<i> light switch clanking</i> )

11:07.375 --> 11:10.878
(<i> circus music playing</i> )

11:12.963 --> 11:15.424
(<i> yawning loudly</i> )

11:15.508 --> 11:18.677
OH, BOY, WHAT A BEAUTIFUL DAY!

11:18.761 --> 11:20.638
(<i> phone rings</i> )

11:20.721 --> 11:22.014
HELLO?

11:22.098 --> 11:24.725
Heffer's voice:
I hate baloney!

11:24.809 --> 11:26.769
(<i> yelling and burbling</i> )

11:29.522 --> 11:32.608
Filburt's voice:
I AM THE CHEESE!

11:32.692 --> 11:35.319
I AM THE BEST CHARACTER
ON THE SHOW.

11:35.403 --> 11:38.489
{\an1}I AM BETTER THAN BOTH THE SALAMI
