<i>NOTICE THE TEXTURE</i>
<i>OF THIS MEAT LOAF. LOAF.</i>

11:52.294 --> 11:54.213
<i>PINEAPPLES GIVE IT</i>
<i>A FESTIVE TOUCH.</i>

11:54.296 --> 11:56.215
(<i> burping</i> )

11:56.298 --> 11:58.509
I AM THE CHEESE.

11:58.592 --> 12:01.137
{\an1}I AM THE BEST CHARACTER
